    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to help with a paper on urban development, specifically focusing on the benefits of high-density zoning and whether its environmental benefits are considered a \"settled fact.\" The assistant initially provides a list of benefits, then claims the environmental benefits are a \"settled matter,\" before finally providing reasons why opponents of high-density zoning hold their views.",
